<%
// Emergency Tree Service Page
%>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/emergency-tree.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Emergency Tree Services in Gold Beach, OR</h1>
        <p>Fast & Reliable Emergency Tree Removal on the Southern Oregon Coast</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="service-detail section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Introduction with Image -->
        <div class="service-intro">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>JT & Sons Tree Service LLC provides fast and professional emergency tree services in Gold Beach, Oregon and nearby communities including Brookings, Pistol River, Ophir, Agnes, Port Orford, Sixes, Langlois, Bandon, and Coos Bay.</p>
                <p>Severe storms, strong coastal winds, and heavy rain can cause trees to fall unexpectedly or create dangerous situations. When a tree becomes unstable or falls on your property, you need a trusted emergency tree service that can respond quickly and safely.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-image">
                <img src="/images/tree-removal.jpg" alt="Emergency Tree Service" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- When You May Need Emergency Tree Services -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>When You May Need Emergency Tree Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Fallen Trees After Storms</strong> – High winds and storms can cause trees or large branches to fall on homes, driveways, vehicles, or power lines.</li>
                <li><strong>Dangerous Hanging Limbs</strong> – Broken branches hanging from trees can fall at any time and create serious safety hazards.</li>
                <li><strong>Leaning or Uprooted Trees</strong> – Trees that suddenly lean or show signs of uprooting after storms may need immediate removal.</li>
                <li><strong>Trees Blocking Roads or Driveways</strong> – Fallen trees can block access to your property and need to be cleared quickly.</li>
                <li><strong>Trees Threatening Structures</strong> – If a tree is leaning toward your home, garage, or building, emergency removal may be required.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose Us + Image Row -->
        <div class="service-include-row">
            <div class="service-list">
                <h2>Why Choose JT & Sons for Emergencies</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Fast Emergency Response</strong> – We respond quickly to emergency tree situations in Gold Beach and Curry County.</li>
                    <li><strong>Experienced Tree Professionals</strong> – With over three decades of experience, we safely handle emergency tree removals of all sizes.</li>
                    <li><strong>Professional Equipment</strong> – Our team uses specialized tools and equipment to safely remove fallen trees and hazardous limbs.</li>
                    <li><strong>Complete Storm Cleanup</strong> – After removing the tree or debris, we ensure your property is cleaned and cleared.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/emergency-tree.jpg" alt="Storm Cleanup" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Process -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Our Emergency Tree Service Process</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Emergency Assessment</strong> – We quickly assess the situation to identify hazards and determine the safest removal plan.</li>
                <li><strong>Safe Tree Removal</strong> – Our trained crew removes the fallen or hazardous tree using professional equipment and controlled techniques.</li>
                <li><strong>Storm Debris Cleanup</strong> – We remove branches, logs, and debris from your property to restore safety and accessibility.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Emergency Contact Box -->
        <div class="contact-info-box emergency">
            <h3>Call Now for Emergency Tree Service</h3>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Office: <a href="tel:<%= sitePhone %>"><%= sitePhone %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> 24/7 Cell: <a href="tel:<%= siteCell %>"><%= siteCell %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: <a href="mailto:<%= siteEmail %>"><%= siteEmail %></a>
            </p>
            <p>Call now to request emergency tree removal or storm damage service.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>